{"tid":750332,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"其實簡迪算係防中定box-to-box？","createTime":"2018-07-20T19:31:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-21T12:58:03.000Z","uid":165817,"like":13,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"dd7d8edb135b77dcb0b80d491b1bb1d26d97b3ab","tid":750332,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T19:31:32.000Z","msg":"防中通常都係極少極少參與進攻<br />\n跑動好撚多 但都係橫向 縱向跑動好少<br />\n<br />\n無論係掃蕩型防中<br />\n例如卡斯米路 迪莊 高基連 迪亞<br />\n定係deep-lying嘅技術型防中<br />\n例如影帝 卡域克 米基爾 阿朗素<br />\n都基本上唔會入對方禁區 好少入波<br />\n<br />\n有啲雖然似防中<br />\n例如韋拉 艾辛 馬度迪 維達爾<br />\n但都明顯分到佢地係b2b<br />\n後上能力強 縱向跑動多 射門腳頭重<br />\n全面性遠勝一般防守中場<br />\n<br />\n簡迪真係唔知偏向邊類<br />\n睇落明明係全職掃蕩型防中<br />\n但向前推進嘅能力亦強 扭波有功架<br />\n係快速反擊嘅第一個起動點<br />\n不過侵略性又唔算好高 又少入禁區<br />\n但活動範圍又大過上面堆真防中好多<br />\n<br />\n車路士奪冠嗰季<br />\n我覺得馬迪先係真正喺後面逗住嗰個<br />\n有少少似以前派路仲深過加度素咁<br />\n但又唔可以話佢唔係防中<br />\n而李城嗰陣 就明顯喺真禾達後面掃<br />\n<br />\n大家又覺得佢係偏向邊一類？"},{"pid":"3be13f89005f4eaac866f9ef88a3cceb619a2e16","tid":750332,"uid":27251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T19:34:37.000Z","msg":"B2B"},{"pid":"4207ca6cdde934a9ffdc59d09a1c11df6a32ad75","tid":750332,"uid":115982,"like":4,"dislike":36,"score":-32,"quote":{"pid":"3be13f89005f4eaac866f9ef88a3cceb619a2e16","tid":750332,"uid":27251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T19:34:37.000Z","msg":"B2B"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T19:38:31.000Z","msg":"2&amp;B"},{"pid":"2138569ec3f7d3725497b79765438e5b2bc28d1d","tid":750332,"uid":172925,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T19:50:30.000Z","msg":"掃蕩型b2b"},{"pid":"2d3953ed465f8b7c3de5e40c506221377e1c9f5c","tid":750332,"uid":102240,"like":0,"dislike":23,"score":-23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T19:56:20.000Z","msg":"第一句就可以顯示到無知"},{"pid":"cac6a23c2dd08feeb2c89b78c0c2d088d3d5cb13","tid":750332,"uid":165817,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2d3953ed465f8b7c3de5e40c506221377e1c9f5c","tid":750332,"uid":102240,"like":0,"dislike":23,"score":-23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T19:56:20.000Z","msg":"第一句就可以顯示到無知"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T20:05:05.000Z","msg":"有咩高見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da78abf458a7ff6a0c766a3eaf35ea7bd7481fb5","tid":750332,"uid":113165,"like":41,"dislike":4,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T20:06:40.000Z","msg":"點解要用一個term黎限死一個球員既作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82114b841209288e1498c553f6d2df68c2be08fc","tid":750332,"uid":165817,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"da78abf458a7ff6a0c766a3eaf35ea7bd7481fb5","tid":750332,"uid":113165,"like":41,"dislike":4,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T20:06:40.000Z","msg":"點解要用一個term黎限死一個球員既作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T20:07:58.000Z","msg":"...我問下佢係偏向邊類型啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e755d39483c4635033fe17b1717630885d4c9e0","tid":750332,"uid":172925,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"82114b841209288e1498c553f6d2df68c2be08fc","tid":750332,"uid":165817,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"da78abf458a7ff6a0c766a3eaf35ea7bd7481fb5","tid":750332,"uid":113165,"like":41,"dislike":4,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T20:06:40.000Z","msg":"點解要用一個term黎限死一個球員既作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T20:07:58.000Z","msg":"...我問下佢係偏向邊類型啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T20:15:42.000Z","msg":"呢啲好死架姐<br />\n冇話啲咩球員一定係果個類型<br />\n每一個球員嘅作用同能力都唔同<br />\n足球係自由架<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d10e29ce4f4458475427daeba403cd7b2e18c734","tid":750332,"uid":94360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82114b841209288e1498c553f6d2df68c2be08fc","tid":750332,"uid":165817,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"da78abf458a7ff6a0c766a3eaf35ea7bd7481fb5","tid":750332,"uid":113165,"like":41,"dislike":4,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T20:06:40.000Z","msg":"點解要用一個term黎限死一個球員既作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T20:07:58.000Z","msg":"...我問下佢係偏向邊類型啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T20:18:54.000Z","msg":"補位中場<br />\n攻守都係做緊補位<br />\n進攻令隊友有安全嘅傳波選擇<br />\n防守當然係不斷斷passing line同截擊<br />\n持球就傳/護送個波俾更有威脅/視野嘅球員<br />\n你見佢帶波都係用速度上前安全俾更有威脅嘅球員<br />\n要有紀律加無限體力先做到<br />\n唔係佢個位上腦俾人斷波好麻煩"},{"pid":"e55cd167be2cf59260e4f77b44371cfdf6be2c92","tid":750332,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T20:25:14.000Z","msg":"似box to box<br />\n<br />\n除左攔截佢帶波同傳波都ok架"},{"pid":"693850ce6d0844c64891cc1a7970ee4ecfd8723d","tid":750332,"uid":47564,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T20:57:01.000Z","msg":"其實個人認為佢係偏防中,佢打B2B嚟講其實喺插上時機,射門能力同俾killer pass嘅能力都唔算頂級. <br />\n<br />\n只不過受身型(背身護波能力)同控制節奏能力所限,馬迪打holding位會嚟得比佢好,而且俾佢打b2b可以更加活用到佢高位反搶嘅能力,所以個人認為佢比較似個防守型b2b,外加帶波上前嘅能力."},{"pid":"5436a9faffcc3dd5b25f1c129e300785df8c7027","tid":750332,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T21:00:13.000Z","msg":"kante已經係球王級中場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b556a4dc34e3b9b61df1d2975a15b0975e952f5","tid":750332,"uid":75193,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T21:01:55.000Z","msg":"越吹越大<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9659b98912fc3ed04366f34f85702aa02d5ec75","tid":750332,"uid":40588,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"4207ca6cdde934a9ffdc59d09a1c11df6a32ad75","tid":750332,"uid":115982,"like":4,"dislike":36,"score":-32,"quote":{"pid":"3be13f89005f4eaac866f9ef88a3cceb619a2e16","tid":750332,"uid":27251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T19:34:37.000Z","msg":"B2B"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T19:38:31.000Z","msg":"2&amp;B"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T21:04:14.000Z","msg":"佢係屬於後備型中場"},{"pid":"cb1c1e4baba4bff207b9fcc92bcec3fb91816e6f","tid":750332,"uid":195989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T21:08:25.000Z","msg":"算防中啦，佢跑動範圍大但唔係B2B，最大體現係好少去到人地禁區"},{"pid":"2c8b6491749ee89b12b4ee153afe1533f3e8e792","tid":750332,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5436a9faffcc3dd5b25f1c129e300785df8c7027","tid":750332,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T21:00:13.000Z","msg":"kante已經係球王級中場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T21:08:30.000Z","msg":"訓唔訓"},{"pid":"cc81d208067fadebe69458cbd27ec7907fce69eb","tid":750332,"uid":7225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T22:11:27.000Z","msg":"能力上佢其實做到b2b, 不過佢既任務係防中"},{"pid":"08bee0d7c419a6aa5ceefe2faf052526bd83f1d7","tid":750332,"uid":51105,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T23:44:20.000Z","msg":"你肯定Casemiro少向前插，入禁區同入波？<br />\n我自己覺得今時今日好似越嚟越少純防守嘅防中<br />\n就好似雙閘咁，以前好多都係助攻到三閘線就差唔多<br />\n依家好多都要做埋叠瓦上去落底線出波，甚至衝埋入禁區<br />\n我覺得Kante同Casemiro呢類球員係介乎def mid同box to box之間，掃蕩能力強，防守時會見到佢哋，同時亦會適當地向前幫拖，並唔係普通box to box咁衝上衝落"},{"pid":"6826d49bdcdc80f4ca9cb63bce5fb6550134ead4","tid":750332,"uid":102240,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"cac6a23c2dd08feeb2c89b78c0c2d088d3d5cb13","tid":750332,"uid":165817,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2d3953ed465f8b7c3de5e40c506221377e1c9f5c","tid":750332,"uid":102240,"like":0,"dislike":23,"score":-23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T19:56:20.000Z","msg":"第一句就可以顯示到無知"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T20:05:05.000Z","msg":"有咩高見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T00:35:28.000Z","msg":"首先搞清楚，進攻唔代表個人一定要跑到入人禁區，或者禁區附近，特別對中場黎講<br />\n<br />\n派路，沙維，恩尼斯達，迪布尼呢類球員最「進攻」果陣係禁區外，甚至係中圈<br />\n<br />\n就算你講果d橫傳係進攻都好緊要，駁腳駁得夠快先有攻勢，可快可慢既中場球員係控制到攻守節奏，你睇馬迪果d搶完個波返黎妹十幾秒，先撥橫交個3米外梗係無進攻啦，你咁慢人地巴士都可以泊，加度素搶完個波3秒到派路腳咪有進攻囉，快過人地turnover<br />\n<br />\n第二搞清楚，除非美斯C7果類踢既所謂「攻中」位，防唔防守中場都係要防守，利上季成隊都會係中場瘋狂搶逼，巴塞都會，自己去whoscore睇下大部份球員攔截數，守波係成隊做，ozil世盃咪就係唔守，但又淨係踢中場果飯，行行企企會好現形（唔係話佢唔岩）"},{"pid":"d8b32a0573bd1e8f2822e1d7be3c71450b5c6eb4","tid":750332,"uid":87394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T01:24:15.000Z","msg":"波唔洗踢到咁死既"},{"pid":"f06de3b36b9e8c004b445ffc7ac37f33bce5297a","tid":750332,"uid":50442,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T01:26:18.000Z","msg":"其實卡斯米路成日都走得前過卻摩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46108aec180b4b09ffdd25d05cd2b76f05a580e1","tid":750332,"uid":54966,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T01:29:58.000Z","msg":"兩者中間<br />\nball winning midfielder<br />\n<br />\n你所講既防中正確d黎講係holding midfielder <br />\n個位置相對比較static<br />\n但簡迪活動範圍大 但同時防守工作出色<br />\n後上跑一段再交波"},{"pid":"d133d6ddc4e7c93b895efd0650ed323c25bc41ca","tid":750332,"uid":51105,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T01:31:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">第一句就可以顯示到無知</span></blockquote>有咩高見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>首先搞清楚，進攻唔代表個人一定要跑到入人禁區，或者禁區附近，特別對中場黎講<br />\n<br />\n派路，沙維，恩尼斯達，迪布尼呢類球員最「進攻」果陣係禁區外，甚至係中圈<br />\n<br />\n就算你講果d橫傳係進攻都好緊要，駁腳駁得夠快先有攻勢，可快可慢既中場球員係控制到攻守節奏，你睇馬迪果d搶完個波返黎妹十幾秒，先撥橫交個3米外梗係無進攻啦，你咁慢人地巴士都可以泊，加度素搶完個波3秒到派路腳咪有進攻囉，快過人地turnover<br />\n<br />\n第二搞清楚，除非美斯C7果類踢既所謂「攻中」位，防唔防守中場都係要防守，利上季成隊都會係中場瘋狂搶逼，巴塞都會，自己去whoscore睇下大部份球員攔截數，守波係成隊做，ozil世盃咪就係唔守，但又淨係踢中場果飯，行行企企會好現形（唔係話佢唔岩）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講咗咁耐，都無講過防中同box to box<br />\n你都係算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dffa494ce254f535deead8682cf922bd87dc60c7","tid":750332,"uid":54966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T01:47:15.000Z","msg":"<strong>Defensive Midfielder\t<br />\nDMC</strong><br />\n\t<br />\nProtects the defensive line from attacks by closing his men down quickly and supporting the creative midfielders in possession<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Anchor\t<br />\nDMC</strong><br />\n\t<br />\nSits in the hole between the defence and midfield, intercepting and winning the ball back and laying off simple passes to his more creative teammates<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Deep Playmaker\t<br />\nDM/M C\t</strong><br />\n<br />\nOperates in the space between the defence and midfield and plays pinpoint long passes to the attackers<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Ball Winning Midfielder\t<br />\nDM/M C\t</strong><br />\n<br />\nCloses down the opposition and win the ball but also helps the team keep possession through his technical skills<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Central Midfielder\t<br />\nMC\t</strong><br />\n<br />\nProvides a link between defence and attack by performing a wide array of tasks<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Box to Box Midfielder\t<br />\nMC</strong>\t<br />\n<br />\nA non-stop dynamic player which he uses to contribute to both defending and attacking<br />\n<br />\n現代足球要球員張張刀周身利 好多人係兩者之間 <br />\n影帝同沙比係anchor 同deep-lying 混合體"}]}